/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"8e6ea43f72e9da2e09e200a432e1bc7a9b002ab8","tid":435573,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要話少睇笑片 又話冇係當時睇過 又要講到自己咁高笑點 例子又比唔出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多巴打reading拎u<br />\n少睇笑片同當時冇睇過有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係少睇笑片都唔覺周星馳好笑 所以覺我佢戲既gag有d過時<br />\n我幾時有講過自己笑點好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例子咪話凸務MADAM好高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f95172deb394f6d6afda11e32b97626f5a66df","tid":435573,"uid":14479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>得喇，知你笑點高喇，好撚勁呀，撚樣！<br />\n咁你又介紹下d好笑戲黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心西遊記燒手,咩愛你一萬年 果D完全笑唔出<br />\n我幾時有話自己好勁<br />\n心平氣和咁帶個題目黎討論 你ON99咁沖出黎做乜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你係咪都係成日講周星馳對白 之後自講自笑果D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我都係想知下你心目中唔脫節既笑片係咩啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你打段野出黎做咩啫？定係你真係俾我講中左你係d以為自己笑點高好撚勁既撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平時睇開台灣綜藝<br />\n我少笑片係事實 最近睇過覺得高汁係凸務MADAM<br />\n關以為自己笑點高咩事 真心唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你既標題同內容就係想同人講：點解全世界人都覺得星爺好笑但係我唔覺得，然後問人點睇？咁我除左話你笑點高都唔知想同你討論d乜好。</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得你依個評語最中肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n討論就係 係咪<span style=\"color: red;\">全世界</span>人都覺得星爺好笑</blockquote><br />\n你計你自己係全世界人呢個範圍入面 咁咪唔係全世界人都覺得星爺好笑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33cb975bfb3152a2fb8e5fc24200d95e430e49f4","tid":435573,"uid":21260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T12:57:10.000Z","msg":"好多都其實幾悲劇 同有意思<br />\n大個睇返係會sad<br />\n有啲真係唔係笑片咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主我驚你單機 同你兜返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a44e1f36e37229d79337734fa2efefd6c845e87","tid":435573,"uid":36167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:00:12.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<br />\n睇戲最緊要有自己睇法<br />\n唔係話周星馳啲戲拍得差<br />\n但事實係佢好大部分嘅笑位我真心笑唔出<br />\n只可以話係口味唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2549dfc4f00225d9a5887cd14bb83c8fed45b57b","tid":435573,"uid":88022,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:00:46.000Z","msg":"咁乜撚野戲叫好笑呀? 答我啦嘛!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cb821df5bc1acc7f52125fc70df53d2ddbe576","tid":435573,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個話西遊記係笑片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西遊sad 撚到仆街喎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">苦海～</span></span>"},{"pid":"56c11709a21c22e0e68fb84a747f71d5cfd8ac4c","tid":435573,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>周星馳啲戲真心垃圾<br />\n樓主推介幾套黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果香港<br />\n<br />\n真心鐘意睇龍咁威多D<br />\n<br />\n低俗喜劇都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n(之後又會有好多人沖出黎話鄭中基,杜汶澤都好笑過周星馳<br />\n我仲好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nok, 樓主品味比較特別"},{"pid":"727df68002c6722b74228e7d2e174a798f48ab4e","tid":435573,"uid":91196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"龍咁威睇左3次已經笑唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但逃學威龍睇左十次以上仲笑得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a32161333e4f1ea1bb1646c36cf85f1a32e3f0","tid":435573,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"樓主肯定睇「喜馬拉亞星」大<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%96%9C%E9%A9%AC%E6%8B%89%E4%BA%9A%E6%98%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%2596%259C%25E9%25A9%25AC%25E6%258B%2589%25E4%25BA%259A%25E6%2598%259F&d=qhykyEhMnRht1cruuPfc5bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7157ab58\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%96%9C%E9%A9%AC%E6%8B%89%E4%BA%9A%E6%98%9F</a>"},{"pid":"5355805418e11f3f7f1c1c4083537761e584ad5d","tid":435573,"uid":26038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:09:37.000Z","msg":"唔止對白笑話<br />\n係整體 表情聲線行為加埋先攪笑<br />\n<br />\n好似而家有條撚屌同星爺把聲好似成日學星爺把聲黎攪gag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知做乜鳩"},{"pid":"bea2a19f628fde070d4d9c3125fbd8ae1475d1b0","tid":435573,"uid":47281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:10:55.000Z","msg":"其實百貨應百客<br />\n每個笑話都有人識笑有人唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星爺逃學威龍回魂夜九品果啲睇親都笑到仆街<br />\n係明知啲gag無厘頭都會笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 非打手 但睇極都唔厭"},{"pid":"29a29af4ae314c6a2bad95c075846021153e093a","tid":435573,"uid":29625,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主讀緊中二？</blockquote><br />\n巴READING拎U?</blockquote><br />\n話你中二病呀柒頭"},{"pid":"b47f0f2385985e8c1ddbbc090f39c3296ed4304f","tid":435573,"uid":124312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:12:00.000Z","msg":"同意樓主"},{"pid":"a80e74a5e68b8132ee0549471972da7691b46240","tid":435573,"uid":56574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:12:56.000Z","msg":"一時話唔好笑 一時又戴頭盔話有d位好笑 你玩撚哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a10829f0b7e7bc1f2f8ae93045e6bcb9ae01ec9","tid":435573,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪以為周星馳全部戲都係笑片？明明西遊記好sad"},{"pid":"0448b65fabf1e93e84ec304d06fd083dcc72bb63","tid":435573,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一時話唔好笑 一時又戴頭盔話有d位好笑 你玩撚哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多連登仔又唔睇人論點又唔爬文<br />\n我一直話緊周星馳既戲 有笑位 <br />\n不過絕對唔係其他人講到咁好笑 冇抖氣位<br />\n有冇人有同感<br />\n<br />\n只係咁簡單<br />\n一早戴左頭盔話知好多人鐘意周星馳 所以會有好多負皮<br />\n我只係講自己睇法<br />\n講同d唔講道理既人講再落去冇意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2248784dad6576ea5da1c7fefec3687cbca9cb4","tid":435573,"uid":56574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:24:55.000Z","msg":"咪話你玩哂囉 點講都無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  開post討論已經無意義 無討論空間"},{"pid":"a5c348b36c369c4878098a9ce0cb8f78a89a2ae4","tid":435573,"uid":22227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:25:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d6c233028f825a2cda5e88f0f9dde86cc023881","tid":435573,"uid":3912,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一時話唔好笑 一時又戴頭盔話有d位好笑 你玩撚哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太多連登仔又唔睇人論點又唔爬文<br />\n我一直話緊周星馳既戲 有笑位 <br />\n不過絕對唔係其他人講到咁好笑 冇抖氣位<br />\n有冇人有同感<br />\n<br />\n只係咁簡單<br />\n一早戴左頭盔話知好多人鐘意周星馳 所以會有好多負皮<br />\n我只係講自己睇法<br />\n講同d唔講道理既人講再落去冇意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你自己標題又話完全唔覺 依家又話有 姐係其實你想點啫 不如你整理下你自己想表達啲咩先再開個post啦好嘛"},{"pid":"4ac18bc531a16284b60bf400c872c6fe951b17f7","tid":435573,"uid":136474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:26:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4417cacd46c92655498343af64a743fe58dc4ac9","tid":435573,"uid":48060,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:28:19.000Z","msg":"你開post 都係想話俾人聽你別樹一幟者<br />\n<br />\n你笑唔出唔係笑點高 而係你個人缺乏幽默感 唔係剩係講先要有幽默感 睇唔睇得明都需要<br />\n樓主睇龍咁威同低俗喜劇呢D 做到出面既笑位咪容易覺得好笑D<br />\n百貨應百客者 直如而家小學生鐘意睇咩笑波子一樣"},{"pid":"d87c6353243fdbf819904c232e5129e84f5c2eba","tid":435573,"uid":56657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:32:50.000Z","msg":"其實星爺d戲勁在翻睇幾多次都唔會厭<br />\n<br />\n每次重播都會忍唔住睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa3b9011ded06b149562e737d3205d66d797bca","tid":435573,"uid":29132,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:33:02.000Z","msg":"樓主 就咁嘅 首先唔討論周星馳好唔好笑 我認為討論失敗你有責任 而唔係單純指責人地唔睇內容<br />\n<br />\n第一件事 你嘅標題係寫完全唔覺 即係指戲入面係引人發笑方面冇任何可取之處 而你內文係寫「係有D位OK 不過絕對唔係其他人講到咁好笑 冇抖氣位」 <br />\n<br />\n問題就嚟啦 咁現家有三個可能性 第一樓主中文唔好<br />\n第二 樓主前言不對後語 第三樓主標題搏出位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  前兩者的話 你不能怪人 第三者的話 你很成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真mode"},{"pid":"72a862fad89d106a6be11023fc12448629d3f2e3","tid":435573,"uid":59101,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"其實周星馳以前嘅電影從藝術方面都有好多值得欣賞嘅地方，而佢果種幽默感都係當時獨一無二嘅<br />\n<br />\n依家果啲笑匠睇落係好笑啲，但佢只係要你為笑而笑，好似食花生咁，但食完就算"},{"pid":"13fa9d02edc5bd4f09efcb4e26a64a49d7f9ede3","tid":435573,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:35:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1de79d9731095a09b358866e6e0572e7503479c9","tid":435573,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecae9e148da255258f112a62a90be580a5c1d5af","tid":435573,"uid":34461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:45:14.000Z","msg":"真假難分"},{"pid":"f1befa86647eef6cc9b4afbffc18209f6a3305c7","tid":435573,"uid":91243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"周星馳好笑不在於啲笑話 係因為佢係周星馳"},{"pid":"4ac2f602099ae7621d0c5b1d7a5ff676369316c7","tid":435573,"uid":14492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"On9樓主"},{"pid":"b220d5345f2aae38b2433737e690308a24434ea7","tid":435573,"uid":113408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"睇樓主心態又係果d睇十個笑話要十個都好笑<br />\n有一個唔好笑=全部唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad3adf07ac9da4bbf8322ce0d0850105a1d4198","tid":435573,"uid":85934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"西遊記唔撚係笑片嚟，係一套大個咗先知原來係好撚悲壯嘅劇情片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccd556493b1518bc31566a33515b83b4192e9ba","tid":435573,"uid":32070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:08:19.000Z","msg":"根本就係樓主啲朋友一齊圍wei喂講周星馳啲對白<br />\n樓主埋唔到堆就唔抵得唯有話人地啲片唔好笑低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251ff27c428782980b08544ec3a1dc53b5615418","tid":435573,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:21:55.000Z","msg":"樓豬新香港人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正常香港人應該由細睇周星馳睇到大<img src=\"/assets/